Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.97,0:24:24.90,Disclaimer,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}This program is a work of fiction.\NAny resemblance to people, parties,\Nor situations is purely coincidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can I not play it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:39.93,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\blur0.5\fs75\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\fnBurst My Bubble KK\b1}Rainy Season Sky {\fnArial}•{\fnBurst My Bubble KK} Quartz Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got your wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ID tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tissues?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Map?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready-to-Eat Meals?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Handgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand grenades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's kidding, Kana!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a moment's thought, you\Nshould have caught on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, you two really have\Nbeen getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio's acting like an overprotective mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the list for today, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! Your mission is to go into town\Nand purchase the supplies on that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having pot-au-feu for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come straight home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time we've gone into\Ntown like this. Right, Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is pretty much my\Nfirst time going into town...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't at all like it was\Nduring the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so calm and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow-ow-ow-ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first was a Nue,\Na roof ornament only found in Trois.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's used to ward off evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other was a drinking fountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,modeled after the twelfth\NHelvetian Archduke, Akira Arcadia II.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You meant what we just saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, you're really smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coming or going?\NMake up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're blocking the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old lady from the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lady, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pressuring people is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not very nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about "Naomi", at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the next shipment's\Nnext month?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, does she know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are some weird girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like any soldiers I've se-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were staring at it the first\Ntime you were here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... C-Can I touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more like a human than a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a marine mammal,\Nback when life still existed in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lived in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old guy's pretty good\Nat making those.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may not look it, but\Nhe's a romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the person\Nwho made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a big factory\Noutside town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All our glasswork\Ncome from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to see them being made.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You're having them make\Nparts for the Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Naomi is getting parts\Nfrom the old era, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're really amazing, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fix a complicated\Nmachine just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:08:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a really hard time memorizing\Nthe codes for the signal trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really not that hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Machines don't betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your change is 2,750,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We get that much back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 2 yen 75 sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as\Nalways, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That morning trumpet...\NIs that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm not very good yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... Well, it really wakes you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking I need to improve so\NI won't bother the townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Seiya, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, I-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come get it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorr-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hit someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}The girl from the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}The clumsy girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you seem\Nto be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya, these people have nothing\Nto do with your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our town!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:10:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing your crap trumpet every morning...\N{\i1}It's annoying!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for his rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a war orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he gets really angry whenever\Nhe sees a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I enlisted, I repeated\Nthe Oath of Paradores.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought I understood that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always understood it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't start whining now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get better in case\Nsomething happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone would be in trouble if there\Nwasn't a signal trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the glass factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a building\Nthat big!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's no good, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the problem with\Noptical aberration?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I've got the\Nright refraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm the new recruit,\NKanata Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how was it until\Nit put up the error?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seek time was\Nessentially the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The distortion along the peripheral\Narea was less than last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss gets really focused when\Nhe starts to talk about work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, he's amazing,\Nold man Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the five people in the nation\Nbearing the title of Meister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won a competition in the capital, and he\Nonce presented his work to the Archduke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria! If there's time for talk,\Nthere's time for work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'm sorry, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not worthy of the\Ntitle, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nothing compared to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lens to the Takemikazuchi's\Noptic sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need two to repair it, so I asked\Nhim to make another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to its primary component\Nof silicon dioxide,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the lens is infused with sodium\Noxide and magnesium oxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This corrects for the chromatic\Nand peripheral aberrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, for the distortion\Nin the captured image.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know how it's distributed\Nthrough the lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a product of the previous\Nera's magic-like technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought glass was just pretty,\Nbut it's complex, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize has high-quality\Nsilica deposits,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's always had a number of small studios\Nthat primarily made works of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was originally one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as the war intensified, the demand grew\Nfor the glass used in military applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This factory prospered\Nbecause of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, I like machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes machines\Nhurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure in the past, the Takemikazuchi\Nkilled a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think a machine that killed\Na lot of people is scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I'm more afraid of the people\Nwho used it than the machine itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this trumpet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I play it, it's awful. But when\NRio plays it, it's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure a tank is the\Nsame kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a while ago, Rio played\Nme a song from inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can make such beautiful music!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's a good tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Why don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she was up all night again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel's working really hard\Nat fixing the Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a real craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she weren't, I wouldn't make something\Nthat's as big a pain in the ass as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, put this on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you guys stopped\Nby Windmill right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said your boss was\Na wonderful romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful. Eh, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He's mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is the technology from\Nthe past that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the boss always says,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You know, no matter how amazing\Nit is, humans just like us made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we could make it, too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You agree, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Or I'd like to say yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Rio's trumpet playing\Nis very different from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I be like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm practicing\Nas hard as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My lips, you see, they're\Nso swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I try and try, but it doesn't\Nsound like hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I really don't have the talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Talent" is the worst excuse cited\Nby people who give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand\Ntrumpets, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do know there's a mistake\Nthe young often make.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, are you trying to force\Nyourself to make the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to make\Nit this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The glass wants to be this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr Carl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sound wants\Nto play itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the sun came\Nup a bit earlier for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a craftsman\Nin her own right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound glass makes\Nchanges slightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,depending on the number of\Nimpurities and their type.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't hear\Nthe difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone with talented\Nears could.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have you\Nlisten for the sound
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's closest to it from the\Nsamples we've made so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, listen to their voices, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she arrived, Noel\Nhas changed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Noel\Nsmile before.
